pdfmerge

Simple utility script using the PyPDF2 library (https://github.com/mstamy2/PyPDF2)
to merge PDF files into one.

Usage: pdfmerge INPUT FILE(S) [-o <OUTPUT FILE>] [-h]

Commands:
	-h - show this help
	-o - specify output file name; default is "out.pdf" 


